content: As an AI language model, I don't have background information of which country you are referring to, nor can I predict what strategies would work best for your country's specific situation. However, the successful strategies implemented by these countries can serve as potential models for other countries. It's important to note that each country's situation and resources are unique, and they would need to consider their specific conditions while adapting any strategies. It's always good to look at successful models and examine how they implemented their effective strategies, but this doesn't mean that these strategies would directly apply to different countries.
